<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>PC Build Recommender</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #0f0f10;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .card {
        background-color: #1a1a1d;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a2f;
        border-radius: 16px;
        max-width: 420px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #fff;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.4rem;
        color: #cfcfd4;
        margin: 0.3rem 0 1rem 0;
      }

      .hint {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #5f5f6a;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg,#3b82f6,#8b5cf6);
        color: white;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="badge">beta</div>
      <h1>PC Build Recommender</h1>
      <p>Ask the bot in the corner: “I have $1500 for Cyberpunk 2077 at 1440p High, build me a PC.”</p>
      <p>It will browse part prices and tell you the best CPU / GPU / RAM for that budget.</p>
      <div class="hint">Look for the chat bubble in the bottom right.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- ChatKit embed -->
    <script src="https://chat.openai.com/static/chatkit/chatkit.js"></script>
    <script>
      window.ChatKit.init({
        workflowId: "WFID_PLACEHOLDER",   // <--- replace this
        version: "1",                     // <--- replace this with the version string you saw
        theme: "dark",
        title: "PC Build AI",
        subtitle: "Get the best gaming rig for your budget.",
        description: "I’ll find recommended specs for your game and price out a full build with estimated FPS.",
        position: "bottom-right"
      });
    </script>
  </body>
